{"tid":2385451,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"城大推「校歌法」「校徽法」， 學生被迫簽保密協議不評論事件","createTime":"2021-01-29T04:58:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-29T11:04:27.000Z","uid":134071,"like":36,"dislike":142,"uniUserReply":88,"replies":[{"pid":"d005bc3915c21fc7c508f53f8a2d22c5f310576e","tid":2385451,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T04:58:55.000Z","msg":"城大推「校歌法」「校徽法」嚴懲損校譽行為 學生簽保密協議不評論事件<br />\n<br />\nBY 劉彥汶<br />\n27/01/2021<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一首諷刺校長在關鍵時候失蹤的歌曲《找郭位》，城市廣播成員懷疑因此被處分。據《立場》去年十一月的報道，其處分為需要被罰者寫道歉信予校方，並在特定時間不得回校。<br />\n<br />\n去年十月底，城市大學教務委員會通過修訂學生守則第4.1.17條，並於十一月二日公布新修訂，新增條款為禁止學生破壞大學品牌及形象的行為，有關「大學品牌及形象」的規禁範圍包括校歌、校徽或任何能代表學校的元素，提高處分，以儆傚尤。<br />\n<br />\n學生形容此例為城大獨有的「校歌法」「校徽法」。學生意難平，在校內竊竊私語諷校長郭位在港版國安法之後，在校內立一條「郭安法」，一條令校方高層安心的校法。校方回應《誌》，表示只是規管學生「利用網路平台發佈虛假消息」，嚴禁造謠。<br />\n<br />\n此例一出，引來學生譁然及不滿，各大新聞平台亦有報道相關修訂條文，但被問到早前是否有學生因一首諷刺城大校長郭位的歌曲而受到校方處分，不論是校媒前首長，還是學生會幹事會前會長，一律統一口徑「我唔評論」。<br />\n<br />\n香港的大學言論自由一再收緊，各學府瀰漫着「敢怒不敢言」的白色恐怖。<br />\n<br />\n【記者劉彥汶報道】<br />\n。。。。<br />\n《誌》向城大校方詢問相關回應，對於新增守則威脅學生的言論自由，城大公關處只表示，對學生「合法的行為和言論持開放態度」，更稱「城大重視學生誠信，嚴禁製造、散播不實謠言」，又指出條例只是禁止學生「利用網路平台發佈虛假消息」，暗示城大校方認為早前二創的作品均為虛假消息。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkfeature.com/%e8%aa%8cnews/1784/%e5%9f%8e%e5%a4%a7%e6%8e%a8%e3%80%8c%e6%a0%a1%e6%ad%8c%e6%b3%95%e3%80%8d%e3%80%8c%e6%a0%a1%e5%be%bd%e6%b3%95%e3%80%8d%e5%9a%b4%e6%87%b2%e6%90%8d%e6%a0%a1%e8%ad%bd%e8%a1%8c%e7%82%ba-%e5%ad%b8%e7%94%9f/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkfeature.com%2F%25e8%25aa%258cnews%2F1784%2F%25e5%259f%258e%25e5%25a4%25a7%25e6%258e%25a8%25e3%2580%258c%25e6%25a0%25a1%25e6%25ad%258c%25e6%25b3%2595%25e3%2580%258d%25e3%2580%258c%25e6%25a0%25a1%25e5%25be%25bd%25e6%25b3%2595%25e3%2580%258d%25e5%259a%25b4%25e6%2587%25b2%25e6%2590%258d%25e6%25a0%25a1%25e8%25ad%25bd%25e8%25a1%258c%25e7%2582%25ba-%25e5%25ad%25b8%25e7%2594%259f%2F&d=lpAVWH70PnqpYPjiCu%2F1w3O0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=91a28eee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkfeature.com/%e8%aa%8cnews/1784/%e5%9f%8e%e5%a4%a7%e6%8e%a8%e3%80%8c%e6%a0%a1%e6%ad%8c%e6%b3%95%e3%80%8d%e3%80%8c%e6%a0%a1%e5%be%bd%e6%b3%95%e3%80%8d%e5%9a%b4%e6%87%b2%e6%90%8d%e6%a0%a1%e8%ad%bd%e8%a1%8c%e7%82%ba-%e5%ad%b8%e7%94%9f/</a>"},{"pid":"3fec2eacfdd1c7c27ce73186882d53b3d993679d","tid":2385451,"uid":134071,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T04:59:10.000Z","msg":"痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b145205fcf5891643c13f56ff17fb0f0a44d4cc","tid":2385451,"uid":134071,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T05:00:22.000Z","msg":"惡撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14f3c3ade5b43a3d815d24ee57e1bcaf0260a42a","tid":2385451,"uid":31296,"like":161,"dislike":2,"score":159,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T05:00:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mUwR97.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmUwR97.jpg&h=e1de010e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3e764ea8187a65ec7f3a1c0dbb38e705d6d474fd","tid":2385451,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14f3c3ade5b43a3d815d24ee57e1bcaf0260a42a","tid":2385451,"uid":31296,"like":161,"dislike":2,"score":159,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T05:00:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mUwR97.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmUwR97.jpg&h=e1de010e&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T05:00:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/swipe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/swipe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/swipe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/swipe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd4d6a536be5625e3aac1dafb6ab0f770ab59589","tid":2385451,"uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T05:01:17.000Z","msg":"痴撚線！"},{"pid":"7db30b12f73f551e8709bd7145127b25d3aa245e","tid":2385451,"uid":134071,"